DESCRIPTION:Wake Up Shabbat is a joyful\, musical\, and engaging service designed especially for young children and their families.\nWhether it’s your first time or you’ve joined us before\, all are welcome to sing along\, connect with friends\, and start the day with community and spirit. \nLight snacks will be available.
