SUMMARY:Tot Shabbat
DESCRIPTION:Come together with Shoresh and Ner Tamid families for an evening of Shabbat fun\, food\, & friendship. We’ll begin with a brief\, clergy-led Tot Shabbat service\, followed by a community potluck Shabbat dinner. All are welcome! \nWe kindly ask each family to bring a dairy/parve\, nut-free side dish or dessert to share. TNT will provide the main entrees. \nLooking forward to celebrating Shabbat with you! \nREGISTER HERE!
URL:https://nertamid.org/event/tot-shabbat-7-2/
CATEGORIES:Worship
END:VEVENT
