SUMMARY:Yom Ha'Atzmaut Potluck Dinner
DESCRIPTION:This Yom Ha’atzmaut\, we invite our community to come together at Temple Ner Tamid on Sunday\, April 19\, from 3:00–5:00pm. \n Even in a difficult time as Israel faces war with Iran\, Independence Day remains a moment to connect\, to support one another\, and to honor Israel’s story and spirit. Join us as we share Israeli music\, activities for kids\, and a meal together—we will provide main dishes and invite you to bring a dairy/parve side dish that reminds you of Israel. Most of all\, this is a chance to be together in community at a time when we especially need one another. \nClick here to register!
URL:https://nertamid.org/event/yom-haatzmaut-potluck-dinner/
CATEGORIES:Holiday
END:VEVENT
