SUMMARY:Seniors Group Meeting
DESCRIPTION:Our very active 65 plus community meets twice monthly on Tuesdays from 11:15-1:15pm for stimulating conversations\, guest speakers\, cultural programming\, holiday celebrations\, Qi Gong exercise and much more. \nThe group is open to Temple Ner Tamid members and parents and friends of members. If you or anyone you know is interested in meeting new people in an inviting atmosphere\, come give us a try! The group is sponsored by Temple Ner Tamid & the JCC Metrowest. \n \n10:45am – 11:15pm – Qi Gong Exercise \n11:15am – 11:45pm – Current Events Discussion\n11:45pm-12:15pm – Lunch (Bring your own dairy lunch. Coffee & cake provided)\n12:15-1:15pm – Program
URL:https://nertamid.org/event/seniors-group-meeting-2/2026-04-21/
CATEGORIES:General
END:VEVENT
